items.title: New Iran videos show bodies piled in hospital and snipers on roofs
items.description: Footage from a hospital in Tehran shows at least 31 bodies piled inside and seven body bags outside.

items.title: Trump abandons attack mode as Minneapolis shooting backlash grows
items.description: The White House has shifted how it talks about Alex Pretti's killing as more Republicans express concern over the deadly encounter.

items.title: Nigerian officers to face trial over coup-plot allegations
items.description: Following an investigation some of the 16 detained last year are accused of planning to unseat President Bola Tinubu.

items.title: Private jet carrying eight people crashes in Maine
items.description: Poor visibility was reported at the airport during a winter storm that has affected a large swathe of the US.
